issue.title: Google Maps URL Generator
issue.body: Create a Google Maps URL generator based on the location and the airport of origin. The generator will have to handle cases where the location is based on current location (when available) (see http://stackoverflow.com/a/37292066) or user provided location

issue.title: Fetching Check Wait Time
issue.body: TSA offers an API to access screening wait time, see: https://www.dhs.gov/mytsa-api-documentation. This should be taken into account with post-screening leisure activities and boarding times to advise the passenger when to line up for screening (along with a 10 min buffer time, if time allows, in that case, the passenger should line up for screening immediately)

issue.title: Remind the user to check-in for the flight
issue.body:
The following template allows for adding iternary references:  https://developers.facebook.com/docs/messenger-platform/send-api-reference/airline-checkin-template

The check-in website will be a from a predefined list of select airlines.
